moonbase is a 2D engine for Lua scripts

Documentation
=============
https://github.com/Protovision/moonbase/wiki

Building on Linux
=================

Make sure you have the following development libraries installed:
SDL2, SDL2 image, SDL2 ttf, SDL2 mixer, talloc, json-c, lua5.2

Run make

Building on Mac
===============

Download the development framework files for SDL2, SDL2 image, SDL2 ttf, and SDL2 mixer.
Copy them to /Library/Frameworks

Run make

Building on Windows
===================

Not supported yet

